{"data": [{"id": "4743113", "title": "Realty Income: Turning Bullish For Once", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499955814/image_1499955814.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Large 7-11 Convenience Building Store with customer service parking lot area against blue sky background at Samut Sakhon, Thailand - March 31, 2023\" data-id=\"1499955814\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"958px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499955814/image_1499955814.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499955814/image_1499955814.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499955814/image_1499955814.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499955814/image_1499955814.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499955814/image_1499955814.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499955814/image_1499955814.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499955814/image_1499955814.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499955814/image_1499955814.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Prapat Aowsakorn</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Discussing <strong>Realty Income Corporation (NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/O\" class=\"ticker-link\">O</a>)</strong> brings excitement due to the real estate investment trust's popularity. Moreover, Realty Income invests with conviction, meaning its incremental talking points are en masse.</p> <p>We <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4680641-realty-income-stock-unlikely-recover-year-to-date-losses-2024\">last covered</a> the REIT in March, where we</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499955814/image_1499955814.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743113-realty-income-turning-bullish-for-once", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 00:07:59"}, {"id": "4743112", "title": "VXUS: 51 Countries Against 1", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172811273/image_2172811273.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"World Map Pacific Center 3D Render Topographic Map Dark Ocean Neutral\" data-id=\"2172811273\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"831px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172811273/image_2172811273.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172811273/image_2172811273.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172811273/image_2172811273.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172811273/image_2172811273.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172811273/image_2172811273.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172811273/image_2172811273.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172811273/image_2172811273.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2172811273/image_2172811273.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fet